{"tid":406089,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人生過骨刺?","createTime":"2017-09-19T11:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T15:40:46.000Z","uid":93874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75da69f18e0a9772c18e5a276e56bfaab7243a11","tid":406089,"uid":93874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:15:57.000Z","msg":"最近阿媽話條腰成日好痛 之後去睇完醫生照完話係條腰位有骨刺 剩係開左d止痛藥俾佢<br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇有經驗巴絲知道食咩藥或者有咩方法根治同埋舒緩下冇咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我阿媽有時已經話痛到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85b220f8d09ccabbfa018eed5cafc78b0ed5bcf","tid":406089,"uid":96829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"係咪差唔多每個人都會生一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我阿媽之前又係要睇醫生同食中西藥，<br />\n之後無啦啦又好返"},{"pid":"d804bc4d3dc9fd73756360c92537f3454bc0e2d0","tid":406089,"uid":73737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d2bce1b4241ca9c42ff52d2b16d19c3a425e06f5","tid":406089,"uid":128953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪差唔多每個人都會生一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我阿媽之前又係要睇醫生同食中西藥，<br />\n之後無啦啦又好返</blockquote><br />\n可以生好多次，生骨刺原因係 關節之間既軟骨(軟組織)磨捐，生多左小小多餘骨出黎。只係勁細既骨仔，就可以痛撚死。<br />\n我地身體咁多關節，全部都會因勞動而磨捐，都有機會生骨刺架。所以人生唔一定只係生一次。<br />\n<br />\n解决方法：<br />\n1，做手術磨左骨刺佢。 <br />\n2(民間傳說)，做多D運動，骨與骨之間既磨擦磨走骨刺，食返D骨膠原修補返關節之間既軟組織。<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係專業人士，最好咨詢醫生或專業人士意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195f0c1b833262dc88fa4123a29bd494d4f51a0f","tid":406089,"uid":93874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquot